"560","<DESCRIPTION>INTERNALCONTROL"
"561","<TEXT>"
"562","REPORT OF INDEPENDENT"
"563","REGISTERED PUBLIC"
"564","ACCOUNTING FIRM"
"565","To the Shareholders and"
"566","Board of Trustees of"
"567","Investment Managers Series Trust"
"568","Glendora, California 91740"
"569","In planning and performing our audit"
"570","of the financial statements of Palmer"
"571","Square SSI Alternative Income Fund"
"572","(the Fund), a series of Investment"
"573","Managers Series Trust, as of and for the"
"574","year ended March 31, 2018, in"
"575","accordance with the standards of the"
"576","Public Company Accounting Oversight"
"577","Board (United States), we considered"
"578","their internal control over financial"
"579","reporting, including control activities for"
"580","safeguarding securities, as a basis for"
"581","designing our auditing procedures for"
"582","the purpose of expressing our opinion"
"583","on the financial statements and to"
"584","comply with the requirements of Form"
"585","N-SAR, but not for the purpose of"
"586","expressing an opinion on the"
"587","effectiveness of the Funds internal"
"588","control over financial reporting."
"589","Accordingly, we express no such"
"590","opinion."
"591","The management of the Fund is"
"592","responsible for establishing and"
"593","maintaining effective internal control"
"594","over financial reporting.  In fulfilling"
"595","this responsibility, estimates and"
"596","judgments by management are required"
"597","to assess the expected benefits and"
"598","related costs of controls.  A companys"
"599","internal control over financial reporting"
"600","is a process designed to provide"
"601","reasonable assurance regarding the"
"602","reliability of financial reporting and the"
"603","preparation of financial statements for"
"604","external purposes in accordance with"
"605","generally accepted accounting"
"606","principles.  A companys internal control"
"607","over financial reporting includes those"
"608","policies and procedures that (1) pertain"
"609","to the maintenance of records that, in"
"610","reasonable detail, accurately and fairly"
"611","reflect the transactions and dispositions"
"612","of the assets of the company; (2) provide"
"613","reasonable assurance that transactions"
"614","are recorded as necessary to permit"
"615","preparation of financial statements in"
"616","accordance with generally accepted"
"617","accounting principles, and that receipts"
"618","and expenditures of the company are"
"619","being made only in accordance with"
"620","authorizations of management and"
"621","directors of the company; and (3)"
"622","provide reasonable assurance regarding"
"623","prevention or timely detection of"
"624","unauthorized acquisition, use or"
"625","disposition of a companys assets that"
"626","could have a material effect on the"
"627","financial statements."
"628","Because of inherent limitations, internal"
"629","control over financial reporting may not"
"630","prevent or detect misstatements.  Also,"
"631","projections of any evaluation of"
"632","effectiveness to future periods are"
"633","subject to the risk that controls may"
"634","become inadequate because of changes"
"635","in conditions, or that the degree of"
"636","compliance with the policies or"
"637","procedures may deteriorate."
"638","A deficiency in internal control over"
"639","financial reporting exists when the"
"640","design or operation of a control does not"
"641","allow management or employees, in the"
"642","normal course of performing their"
"643","assigned functions, to prevent or detect"
"644","misstatements on a timely basis.  A"
"645","material weakness is a deficiency, or"
"646","combination of deficiencies, in internal"
"647","control over financial reporting, such"
"648","that there is a reasonable possibility that"
"649","a material misstatement of the companys"
"650","annual or interim financial statements"
"651","will not be prevented or detected on a"
"652","timely basis."
"653","To the Shareholders and"
"654","Board of Trustees of"
"655","Investment Managers Series Trust"
"656","Page Two"
"657","Our consideration of the Funds internal"
"658","control over financial reporting was for"
"659","the limited purpose described in the first"
"660","paragraph and would not necessarily"
"661","disclose all deficiencies in internal"
"662","control that might be material"
"663","weaknesses under standards established"
"664","by the Public Company Accounting"
"665","Oversight Board (United States)."
"666","However, we noted no deficiencies in"
"667","the Funds internal control over financial"
"668","reporting and its operation, including"
"669","controls for safeguarding securities,"
"670","which we consider to be material"
"671","weaknesses, as defined above, as of"
"672","March 31, 2018."
"673","This report is intended solely for the"
"674","information and use of management,"
